    Given I obtain test data file "routing/abrouting/abtest-websrv2.yaml"
    When I run the :create client command with:
      | f | abtest-websrv2.yaml |
    Then the step should succeed
    And a pod becomes ready with labels:
      | name=abtest-websrv2 |
