    When I expose the "service-unsecure" service
    Then the step should succeed
    When I run the :annotate client command with:
      | resource     | route                                          |
      | resourcename | service-unsecure                               |
      | overwrite    | true                                           |
      | keyval       | haproxy.router.openshift.io/balance=roundrobin |
    Then the step should succeed
